verbose_text: Other non tyrosine kinases, such as Btk and Etk within the Tek family of non tyrosine kinases, are being targeted as well; recent work by Guo and colleagues demonstrated that CTN06, a novel dual inhibitor of Btk and Etk, induced apoptosis and autophagy, and also re-sensitized cell lines to docetaxel.
evidence: CTN06, a novel dual inhibitor of Btk and Etk, induced apoptosis
